Challenges
========================================================
type: exclaim

Moving on to the machine learning process, there was a significant challenge in improving the model to be sufficently accurate.
- Low predictive variable count

- Data from multiple companies instead of a single company

Solutions
========================================================
type: exclaim

- Stratification

- ROSE

- Stacking

Final Points
========================================================
type: exclaim

- Improvements from 50% to 80% to 88% based on methods used to accomodate for the under represented class

- This data serves as an interesting look at a workplace culture in numeric form, which is the most powerful predictive variable for this topic

- While successful in its intent, it is important to seek more realistic, company specific forms of data to proceed with further analysis